ence of hypocrisy?\u201d Abu Darda said, \u201cIt is that you see the body in reverence, but the heart is not reverent.\u201d Source:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":4206,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/08\/05\/duties-allah-selves-family\/","url_meta":{"origin":8766,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Duties: Rights of Allah, your family, and yourself","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 5, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Juhayfah reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, made a fellowship between Salman and Abu Darda. Salman visited Abu Darda and found his wife Umm Darda dressed in worn-out clothing. He asked her why she was like this. She said, \u201cYour brother Abu Darda is not interested\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":28586,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/05\/01\/be-scholar-student-devotee-follower\/","url_meta":{"origin":8766,"position":4},"title":"Abu Darda on Knowledge: Be a scholar, student, devotee, or follower","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 1, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Hasan reported: Abu Darda, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cBe a scholar, a student, a devotee, or a follower; do not be the fifth type lest you be ruined.\u201d It was said to Al-Hasan, \u201cWho is the fifth type?\u201d Al-Hasan said, \u201cA heretic.\u201d Source: al-Madkhal ila\u0304 al-Sunan al-Kubra\u0301\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":31814,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/08\/prophet-plays-with-zaynab\/","url_meta":{"origin":8766,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Kids: The Prophet plays with Zaynab bint Umm Salamah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 8, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, would play with Zaynab, the daughter of Umm Salamah. The Prophet would keep saying, \u201cO Zaynab! O Zaynab!\u201d Source: al-Ah\u0323a\u0304di\u0304th al-Mukhta\u0304rah 1580 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Suyuti \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0633\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0645\u064e\u0627\u0644\u0650\u0643\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0643\u064e\u0627\u0646\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0651\u064f \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/8766","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable